description: I started my hunt in my favorite shopping center. Already the second guy I met seemed to be interested in my immoral offers. I talked him into jerking me off for 3.000 Crowns. We went to his apartment but he somehow started to change his mind. Well, he already had my dick in his hand when he decided to cancel our little deal. Tough shit. Anyway, then I went to the park where I saw a young man apparently going home from the supermarket. He was a bit shy in the beginning. But I finally persuaded him to follow me to my apartment. We took the tram because I wanted to check if he is really sure about this. I didn´t want such a shameful defeat again:-) And well... what can I say: "Honza victor est!"
title: Czech Hunter 56
